text:
Two men have been arrested after trying to resell 1 million N95 masks in NYC at a 50% markup during the #COVID19 pandemic.

The DOJ says it will not allow "greedy profiteers to take advantage of the public during this health crisis." https://t.co/o3JPn4EAil
